{% call getstarted.section("Overview") -%}

  <p>The <em>design system kit</em> is an Adobe XD library of themed colors, character styles, and components used to design Red Hat web properties. Based on the foundations of <a href="https://www.patternfly.org/v4/">PatternFly</a> and the <a href="https://www.redhat.com/en/about/brand/standards">Red Hat Brand Standards</a>, the design system kit enables users to design consistent experiences that reflect the Red Hat brand digitally.</p>

